# UI Patterns

## Dark theme only

Always use `ctk.set_appearance_mode("Dark")`. All surface colors from `ui.theme`:

```python
from ui import theme

card = ctk.CTkFrame(parent, fg_color=theme.BG_CARD, corner_radius=10,
                     border_width=1, border_color=theme.BORDER)
```

## Card pattern

Every section is a card: `corner_radius=10`, `border_width=1`, `border_color=theme.BORDER`, `fg_color=theme.BG_CARD`. Inner content padded with `padx=20`.

## Charts

```python
fig = Figure(figsize=(5, 2.2), dpi=100)
ax = fig.add_subplot(111)
theme.style_figure(fig)  # MUST call after adding axes
canvas = FigureCanvasTkAgg(fig, master=card)
canvas.get_tk_widget().configure(bg=theme.CHART_BG, highlightthickness=0)
canvas.draw_idle()  # use draw_idle(), never draw()
```

## Status bar updates

Use `_sb_set()` in app.py to avoid flicker — only reconfigure when value changes.

## Hidden networks

Filter networks with null SSID from display. Show "X visible, Y hidden" count in the header.

## Scrolling

Keep the top section (PHY bar + chart + AP card) fixed/visible. Only secondary content (factors, channels, networks) goes in a scrollable frame.
